  &lt;/a&gt;
  
  
  
  
    
      
    
  
  &lt;a data-fancybox=&#34;gallery-UI&#34;  href=&#34;http://jackv24.github.io/img/dungeon-options.png&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img alt=&#34;&#34; src=&#34;http://jackv24.github.io/img/dungeon-options.png&#34;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
  
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;visual-effects&#34;&gt;Visual Effects&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I was also responsible for writing all of the shaders we use throughout the game. This includes a foliage shader for rendering swaying grass and trees, a ground shader for tiling UVs based on world position, a spinning shader for quicksand, and a simple flashing shader for indicating character damage.&lt;/p&gt;



